    <h1 class="title-case-study">Delivering Actionable Insights</h1>

    <div class="collage-text formatting">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <p>It has never been an easier to instrument, collect, and store vast quantities of information. Despite the clear business value of collecting this data, folks still wonder how best to apply it. What does it mean? Can it give decision-makers and users the information they need to be more effective? The challenge in analytics is no longer the logistics of data collection, but rather translating data into actionable recommendations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <p>Following the success of <a href="{{pathFor 'what'}}/verso">Verso</a>, we reconvened with our education partners to tackle a new challenge. While Verso app helped students become lifelong learners by sparking their curiosity, we saw that the breadth and depth of our engagement data could revolutionize teaching school-wide. Campus made use of our integrated design, engineering, and strategy practice to help schools identify & replicate successful teaching.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
</header>

